sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Admin
    participant API as Subscription API
    participant SP as SubscriptionPlan Service
    participant Stripe as Stripe API
    participant DB as MongoDB

    A->>API: POST /subscription-plans/
    API->>A: Authenticate (Admin)
    
    A->>API: Create Plan (name, price, features)
    API->>SP: Validate plan data
    
    SP->>SP: Create Stripe Product
    SP->>Stripe: products.create()
    Stripe-->>SP: stripe_product_id
    
    SP->>Stripe: prices.create()
    Stripe-->>SP: stripe_price_id
    
    SP->>DB: Save SubscriptionPlan
    DB-->>SP: Plan created
    
    SP-->>API: Plan created successfully
    API-->>A: Return plan with IDs
